
msgid "Tarantool 2.10.2"
msgstr ""

msgid "Released on 2022-09-01."
msgstr ""

msgid "Release: :tarantool-release:`2.10.2`."
msgstr ""

msgid "Tag: ``2.10.2``."
msgstr ""

msgid "Overview"
msgstr ""

msgid ""
"2.10.2 is the third :doc:`stable </release/policy/>` version of the 2.10 "
"release series. It introduces 1 improvement and resolves 8 bugs since "
"2.10.1."
msgstr ""

msgid ""
"The “stable” label means that we have all planned features implemented and "
"we see no high-impact issues. However, if you encounter an issue, feel free "
"to `report it <https://github.com/tarantool/tarantool/issues>`__ on GitHub."
msgstr ""

msgid "Compatibility"
msgstr ""

msgid ""
"Tarantool 2.x is backward compatible with Tarantool 1.10.x in the binary "
"data layout, client-server protocol, and replication protocol."
msgstr ""

msgid ""
"Please :doc:`upgrade </book/admin/upgrades>` using the "
"``box.schema.upgrade()`` procedure to unlock all the new features of the 2.x"
" series."
msgstr ""

msgid "Functionality added or changed"
msgstr ""

msgid "Core"
msgstr ""

msgid ""
"Certain internal fibers, such as the connection’s worker fiber, vinyl "
"fibers, and some other fibers, cannot be cancelled from the Lua public API "
"anymore (:tarantool-issue:`7473`)."
msgstr ""

msgid "Bugs fixed"
msgstr ""

msgid ""
"Fixed a crash of secondary indexes without hints (a critical regression "
"found in 2.10.1) (:tarantool-issue:`7605`)."
msgstr ""

msgid ""
"Fixed a possible crash on concurrent ``fiber_object:join()`` (:tarantool-"
"issue:`7489`)."
msgstr ""

msgid ""
"Fixed a potential nil dereference and a crash in case of an active log "
"rotation during the program exit stage (:tarantool-issue:`4450`)."
msgstr ""

msgid ""
"Fixed crashes and undefined behaviour of triggers clearing other triggers "
"(:tarantool-issue:`4264`)."
msgstr ""

msgid "Replication"
msgstr ""

msgid ""
"Fixed ``box.info.replication[id].downstream.lag`` growing indefinitely on a "
"server when it’s not writing any new transactions (:tarantool-issue:`7581`)."
msgstr ""

msgid "Box"
msgstr ""

msgid ""
"Fixed multiline commands being saved to ``~/.tarantool_history`` as separate"
" lines (:tarantool-issue:`7320`)."
msgstr ""

msgid ""
"Fixed inheritance of field options in indexes when index parts are specified"
" the old Tarantool 1.6 style: ``{<field>, <type>, ...}`` (:tarantool-"
"issue:`7614`)."
msgstr ""

msgid ""
"Fixed unauthorized inserts into the ``_truncate`` space (:tarantool-sec-"
"issue:`5`)."
msgstr ""
